entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You removed some of the vermin from the bunker that Lejo Daramus wants to use as his research base.
entries.journal_entry_description: A scientist named Lejo Daramus would like you to help rid a bunker of vermin so that he can use it for his research.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Remove some fiendish durni from the bunker for Lejo Daramus.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Remove some Fiendish Durni from the Bunker
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Lejo Daramus and let him know that you've removed some of the vermin from the bunker.
